title: It's Not Cheap To Be French!
itunes:title: It's Not Cheap To Be French!
description:
FRI 9/2 - The Breakfast Club discusses cheap dates! Could you be in a relationship with someone who hesitates to spend money on you? Speaking of dating, we had to resurrect "Ho Appreciation Day" in honor of French Montana adding to his roster of industry takedowns. Plus Cam Newton gets a hee-haw for doing more dancing than last year around this Kaepernick topic!
